No. 82,

Misc.

Wong Sun et al. v. United States. Sol A. Abrams for petitioners. Solicitor General Cox, Assistant Attorney General Miller, Beatrice Rosenberg and Julia P. Cooper for the United States.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit granted. Case transferred to appellate docket.
